WITH source_data AS (
    SELECT 
        cust_id,
        first_name,
        last_name,
        signup_date,
        is_vip_flag
    FROM demo_db.raw.raw_customers
),

transformed AS (
    SELECT
        -- Direct mapping with type casting
        CAST(cust_id AS STRING) AS customer_id,
        
        -- Concatenate first_name and last_name to create full_name
        CAST(CONCAT(COALESCE(first_name, ''), ' ', COALESCE(last_name, '')) AS STRING) AS full_name,
        
        -- Extract month name from signup_date
        CAST(MONTHNAME(signup_date) AS STRING) AS signup_month,
        
        -- Convert Y/N flag to boolean
        CASE 
            WHEN UPPER(is_vip_flag) = 'Y' THEN TRUE
            WHEN UPPER(is_vip_flag) = 'N' THEN FALSE
            ELSE NULL
        END AS is_vip
        
    FROM source_data
)

SELECT * FROM transformed

WITH source_data AS (
    SELECT 
        emp_id,
        salary
    FROM demo_db.raw.raw_employees
),

transformed AS (
    SELECT
        -- Direct mapping of emp_id to employee_id
        CAST(emp_id AS STRING) AS employee_id,
        
        -- Calculate 15% of salary as annual bonus
        CAST(salary * 0.15 AS FLOAT) AS annual_bonus
        
    FROM source_data
)

SELECT * FROM transformed

WITH source_data AS (
    SELECT 
        product_id,
        quantity
    FROM demo_db.raw.raw_inventory
),

transformed AS (
    SELECT 
        CAST(product_id AS STRING) AS product_id,
        CASE 
            WHEN quantity > 0 THEN 'IN_STOCK'
            ELSE 'OUT_OF_STOCK'
        END AS stock_status
    FROM source_data
)

SELECT * FROM transformed

WITH source_orders AS (
    SELECT 
        order_id,
        customer_id,
        order_date,
        total_amount
    FROM demo_db.raw.raw_orders
),

transformed_orders AS (
    SELECT 
        -- Direct mapping for order_id
        CAST(order_id AS STRING) AS order_id,
        
        -- Direct mapping for customer_id
        CAST(customer_id AS STRING) AS customer_id,
        
        -- Derive ISO week from order_date
        TO_VARCHAR(DATE_PART('WEEK', order_date)) AS order_week,
        
        -- Convert from INR to USD (assuming conversion rate of 0.012)
        CAST(total_amount * 0.012 AS FLOAT) AS total_amount_usd
        
    FROM source_orders
)

SELECT * FROM transformed_orders

WITH source_data AS (
    SELECT 
        payment_id,
        payment_mode
    FROM demo_db.raw.raw_payments
),

transformed AS (
    SELECT 
        CAST(payment_id AS STRING) AS payment_id,
        CASE 
            WHEN UPPER(payment_mode) IN ('CREDIT_CARD', 'DEBIT_CARD', 'CARD') THEN 'Card'
            WHEN UPPER(payment_mode) IN ('DIGITAL_WALLET', 'WALLET', 'PAYPAL', 'GPAY', 'PAYTM') THEN 'Wallet'
            WHEN UPPER(payment_mode) IN ('CASH', 'COD') THEN 'Cash'
            ELSE 'Cash'
        END AS payment_category
    FROM source_data
)

SELECT * FROM transformed

WITH source_data AS (
    SELECT 
        product_id,
        price,
        category
    FROM demo_db.raw.raw_products
),

transformed AS (
    SELECT 
        CAST(product_id AS STRING) AS product_id,
        CASE 
            WHEN UPPER(category) = 'SEASONAL' 
            THEN CAST(price * 0.9 AS FLOAT)
            ELSE CAST(price AS FLOAT)
        END AS discounted_price
    FROM source_data
)

SELECT * FROM transformed

WITH source_reviews AS (
    SELECT 
        review_id,
        rating
    FROM demo_db.raw.raw_reviews
),

transformed_reviews AS (
    SELECT 
        review_id::STRING AS review_id,
        CASE 
            WHEN rating >= 4 THEN 'Positive'
            WHEN rating = 3 THEN 'Neutral'
            ELSE 'Negative'
        END AS sentiment_category
    FROM source_reviews
    WHERE review_id IS NOT NULL
)

SELECT * FROM transformed_reviews

WITH source_data AS (
    SELECT 
        shipment_id,
        delivery_date,
        order_date
    FROM demo_db.raw.raw_shipments
),

transformed AS (
    SELECT
        -- Direct mapping
        CAST(shipment_id AS STRING) AS shipment_id,
        
        -- Calculate delivery delay in days
        CAST(DATEDIFF('day', order_date, delivery_date) AS INTEGER) AS delivery_delay_days,
        
        -- Keep original dates for reference
        delivery_date,
        order_date
        
    FROM source_data
)

SELECT * FROM transformed

WITH source_data AS (
    SELECT 
        transaction_id,
        amount
    FROM demo_db.raw.raw_transactions
),

transformed AS (
    SELECT 
        CAST(transaction_id AS STRING) AS transaction_id,
        CAST(amount * 1.18 AS FLOAT) AS amount_with_tax
    FROM source_data
)

SELECT * FROM transformed

WITH source_data AS (
    SELECT 
        session_id,
        timestamp,
        url
    FROM demo_db.raw.raw_web_logs
),

transformed AS (
    SELECT
        -- Direct mapping for session_id
        session_id::STRING AS session_id,
        
        -- Extract hour from timestamp
        EXTRACT(HOUR FROM timestamp)::INTEGER AS session_hour,
        
        -- Extract domain from URL using string split
        SPLIT_PART(url, '/', 3)::STRING AS domain_name
        
    FROM source_data
    WHERE session_id IS NOT NULL
)

SELECT * FROM transformed
